  "title": "首篇具身智能机器人「安全」综述：LLM 如何跨越物理鸿沟？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652666007&idx=3&sn=c1f849cd06a45f5f2326553623dbc10d",
  "date": "2026-01-20 05:04:00",
